00:03:47.550 --> 00:03:50.420
it allowed for
the transmission of the word of god,

53
00:03:50.420 --> 00:03:55.740
as they the faithful understood
the word and understood God.

54
00:03:55.740 --> 00:04:00.520
And it transmitted the theology,
the message of the church.

