00:05:27.690 --> 00:05:30.760
just one syllable of text.

76
00:05:30.760 --> 00:05:37.530
And in melismatic chant, the range tends
to be a lot broader, it's more virtuosic.

77
00:05:37.530 --> 00:05:42.610
So simple chanting for readings,
